## Non-Negotiable Standards

- **Desktop-first** — design for 1280px wide; then add responsive breakpoints down to tablet (768px)
- **UK English** — all visible text in the UI (labels, tooltips, placeholders, notifications)
- **WCAG AA** — minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio, keyboard accessibility, proper ARIA attributes
- **Brand consistency** — follow GPTW colour palette and typography in every component
- **No inline styles** — use Tailwind utility classes or SCSS variables; avoid `style=""` attributes
